WEBVTT

00:00:30.850 --> 00:00:33.330
[You Have My Heart]

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:36.330
[Episode 22 Meeting demons and gods]

00:00:44.670 --> 00:00:45.600
My Lord, My Lady,

00:00:45.820 --> 00:00:47.020
What should we do now?

00:00:47.110 --> 00:00:48.560
It's complete chaos outside.

00:00:48.560 --> 00:00:49.670
People are insane.

00:00:49.690 --> 00:00:50.410
They fight,

00:00:50.560 --> 00:00:51.280
Rob,

00:00:51.280 --> 00:00:51.970
And set fires.

00:00:51.970 --> 00:00:53.960
The relationship between humans and demons is tense.

00:00:53.960 --> 00:00:55.410
Many spirits have abandoned their livelihoods

00:00:55.410 --> 00:00:57.110
And fled back to the mountains to save their lives.

00:00:57.110 --> 00:00:59.350
The most critical issue is the overwhelming evil power.

00:00:59.350 --> 00:01:02.030
Many seals have already shown signs of instability.

00:01:02.030 --> 00:01:03.430
Many weak spirits

00:01:03.430 --> 00:01:05.870
Lost their spiritual power due to fear.

00:01:05.890 --> 00:01:06.860
The top priority

00:01:06.890 --> 00:01:08.370
Is to re-establish order.

00:01:19.740 --> 00:01:21.450
Open the door! Hurry!

00:01:21.480 --> 00:01:22.480
Open the door!

00:01:22.500 --> 00:01:23.030
Open up!

00:01:23.710 --> 00:01:24.430
Hurry up, open the door!

00:01:24.430 --> 00:01:24.760
Hurry up and beat the drum!

00:01:24.760 --> 00:01:25.760
Hurry up!

00:01:26.420 --> 00:01:27.150
Give it to me.

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:29.200
Dad.

00:01:29.220 --> 00:01:29.680
Don't be afraid.

00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:30.530
I'm scared.

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:34.800
Hurry! Hurry!

00:01:36.479 --> 00:01:37.039
Hurry up!

00:01:40.450 --> 00:01:46.530
Open the door!

00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:47.630
Lady Fufeng!

00:01:47.650 --> 00:01:49.700
Protect us! Lady Fufeng, bless us!

00:01:50.020 --> 00:01:52.020
Lady Fufeng, bless us!

00:01:52.050 --> 00:01:54.180
Open the door!

00:01:56.710 --> 00:01:57.759
Move! Move!

00:01:57.759 --> 00:01:58.430
This is mine!

00:01:58.430 --> 00:01:59.509
This is mine!

00:02:00.530 --> 00:02:01.220
Get away!

00:02:04.380 --> 00:02:06.300
Lady Fufeng!

00:02:09.250 --> 00:02:10.660
Lady Fufeng!

00:02:11.090 --> 00:02:14.140
Open the door! Hurry up!

00:02:14.170 --> 00:02:15.560
Save us!

00:02:16.520 --> 00:02:17.990
Lady Fufeng!

00:02:18.010 --> 00:02:18.910
Open the door!

00:02:33.630 --> 00:02:34.430
Master,

00:02:34.500 --> 00:02:36.560
There are still people asking us for help.

00:02:36.560 --> 00:02:38.570
There are still people willing to trust us.

00:02:38.570 --> 00:02:39.170
My Lady,

00:02:39.440 --> 00:02:40.640
What should we do now?

00:02:41.470 --> 00:02:42.600
Pass down the order.

00:02:42.740 --> 00:02:44.000
Have all spirit envoys

00:02:44.100 --> 00:02:45.510
And willing spirits

00:02:45.530 --> 00:02:46.480
Prepare spiritual spring water

00:02:46.480 --> 00:02:47.579
And sprinkle it all over Yin-Yang Crossing

00:02:47.579 --> 00:02:48.910
After seeing my signal.

00:02:49.520 --> 00:02:50.310
Master,

00:02:50.710 --> 00:02:51.570
What are you...

00:02:51.910 --> 00:02:54.470
We don't have time to comfort the public one by one,

00:02:54.470 --> 00:02:55.710
Nor do we have the strength

00:02:55.710 --> 00:02:58.079
To deal with the evil power of the whole city.

00:02:58.079 --> 00:03:01.190
This ancient willow is connected to the leylines of Yin-Yang Crossing.

00:03:01.190 --> 00:03:03.590
It can reach everywhere from this one spot.

00:03:04.360 --> 00:03:06.800
So, I have a solution.

00:03:17.280 --> 00:03:19.810
I'll connect my origin to the ancient willow,

00:03:20.079 --> 00:03:22.200
And spread the purest purifying power

00:03:22.200 --> 00:03:23.760
Through every branch

00:03:24.079 --> 00:03:25.540
And every leaf of the willow

00:03:25.540 --> 00:03:27.260
Over Yin-Yang Crossing.

00:03:29.170 --> 00:03:30.430
You can't do this, Master!

00:03:30.430 --> 00:03:32.630
It will drain you completely.

00:03:33.160 --> 00:03:34.310
Covering the whole city?

00:03:34.310 --> 00:03:35.710
Then, your spiritual power...

00:03:35.710 --> 00:03:37.360
I can't do it on my own

00:03:38.570 --> 00:03:40.170
Even if

00:03:40.930 --> 00:03:42.930
I deplete the strength of my origin.

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:44.430
But now,

00:03:46.470 --> 00:03:47.270
I have you.

00:03:47.829 --> 00:03:49.630
Our spiritual power shares the same origin,

00:03:49.630 --> 00:03:51.380
And half a heart is beating here.

00:03:51.380 --> 00:03:52.230
Perhaps,

00:03:52.910 --> 00:03:54.000
We can give it a try.

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:57.150
But the cost is

00:03:57.630 --> 00:03:59.730
That I might exhaust all my spiritual power,

00:03:59.730 --> 00:04:01.330
Becoming just like a mortal,

00:04:01.710 --> 00:04:02.560
Or perhaps

00:04:03.680 --> 00:04:05.140
Things will be even worse.

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:26.290
What should I do?

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:35.240
Give me your hand.

00:05:23.190 --> 00:05:24.960
Open the door. Open it.

00:05:27.790 --> 00:05:29.040
Give it to me. Let go.

00:05:29.060 --> 00:05:30.450
This is mine.

00:05:31.200 --> 00:05:32.290
This is mine.

00:05:33.390 --> 00:05:33.950
Mine.

00:05:53.340 --> 00:05:54.670
Thank you, Lady Fufeng.

00:05:54.750 --> 00:05:56.080
Thank you, Lady Fufeng.

00:06:08.720 --> 00:06:09.520
This way,

00:06:10.490 --> 00:06:12.150
There will be no more worries.

00:06:15.450 --> 00:06:16.050
Fufeng.

00:07:04.370 --> 00:07:05.370
Fufeng.

00:07:08.170 --> 00:07:09.660
You can't die.

00:07:13.690 --> 00:07:15.210
You can't die.

00:07:34.460 --> 00:07:37.090
[Fufeng Temple]

00:08:19.700 --> 00:08:20.780
Look.

00:08:25.190 --> 00:08:27.430
Why is the spiritual willow withered?

00:08:28.750 --> 00:08:30.360
That's because Lady Fufeng

00:08:31.390 --> 00:08:33.000
Exhausted her spiritual power

00:08:33.000 --> 00:08:34.400
To protect the whole city

00:08:35.400 --> 00:08:37.200
And blocked the disaster for us.

00:08:37.480 --> 00:08:39.600
Touch your chests now.

00:08:40.909 --> 00:08:42.169
Is it still congested?

00:08:42.270 --> 00:08:43.669
Are you still panicking?

00:08:44.120 --> 00:08:46.320
The reason we are still breathing today

00:08:47.030 --> 00:08:47.960
Is because

00:08:48.840 --> 00:08:50.030
Lady Fufeng

00:08:50.050 --> 00:08:52.410
Spared no efforts to save us last night,

00:08:52.990 --> 00:08:54.940
Amidst the thick black smoke

00:08:54.970 --> 00:08:56.020
Filling the sky.

00:08:56.600 --> 00:08:58.030
Without Lady Fufeng,

00:08:58.350 --> 00:08:59.780
We wouldn't be here.

00:09:02.440 --> 00:09:03.550
Let us

00:09:04.390 --> 00:09:06.750
Pray to the heavens together.

00:09:10.170 --> 00:09:12.810
May God bless Lady Fufeng

00:09:12.960 --> 00:09:14.560
With safety and well-being.

00:09:15.480 --> 00:09:18.120
May Lady Fufeng be safe and sound.

00:09:55.890 --> 00:09:57.650
Lady Fufeng saved my life,

00:09:58.240 --> 00:09:59.910
And Lord Bai gave us justice.

00:10:00.560 --> 00:10:01.960
If they are evil spirits,

00:10:02.840 --> 00:10:04.080
Is there any justice left in this world?

00:10:04.080 --> 00:10:04.740
Be careful.

00:10:05.320 --> 00:10:06.080
Sweep this up.

00:10:06.080 --> 00:10:06.480
Okay.

00:10:13.600 --> 00:10:14.000
Here.

00:10:16.550 --> 00:10:17.200
Okay.

00:10:18.210 --> 00:10:19.570
Let me water you.

00:10:20.550 --> 00:10:22.010
You might just be thirsty.

00:10:25.480 --> 00:10:26.720
One, two, go.

00:10:28.090 --> 00:10:28.600
Come on.

00:10:37.540 --> 00:10:39.570
You youngsters don't know that

00:10:39.910 --> 00:10:41.840
I have lived long enough.

00:10:42.240 --> 00:10:43.840
I know exactly what Lady Fufeng

00:10:43.840 --> 00:10:45.120
Has done for us.

00:10:45.120 --> 00:10:46.680
A bawd doesn't deserve to say this.

00:10:46.680 --> 00:10:48.220
We all know what kind of shady business

00:10:48.220 --> 00:10:49.680
Huichun Brothel is doing.

00:10:49.910 --> 00:10:50.720
Stop!

00:10:50.910 --> 00:10:52.240
I am telling the truth!

00:10:52.380 --> 00:10:54.410
Lady Fufeng set a rule long ago that

00:10:54.510 --> 00:10:57.000
Anyone who forces women into prostitution or forces trades,

00:10:57.000 --> 00:10:57.840
Whether it is a human or a demon,

00:10:57.840 --> 00:10:59.370
Will be strictly punished.

00:10:59.400 --> 00:11:02.010
The girls in our Huichun Brothel only perform.

00:11:02.040 --> 00:11:03.830
They earn a living with their skills.

00:11:03.830 --> 00:11:05.160
Since your heart is dirty,

00:11:05.160 --> 00:11:06.760
Everything you see is dirty.

00:11:07.020 --> 00:11:08.420
You said Lady Fufeng

00:11:08.840 --> 00:11:09.720
Is a demon

00:11:10.150 --> 00:11:11.200
And she stole someone's heart.

00:11:11.200 --> 00:11:12.210
Where is the evidence?

00:11:12.210 --> 00:11:13.660
Show us the evidence.

00:11:15.070 --> 00:11:16.100
If you do not have evidence,

00:11:16.100 --> 00:11:17.360
You can be deemed as spreading rumors

00:11:17.360 --> 00:11:18.540
And confusing the public.

00:11:18.540 --> 00:11:18.880
Yes.

00:11:18.910 --> 00:11:19.600
According to the law,

00:11:19.600 --> 00:11:20.510
You should be slapped.

00:11:20.510 --> 00:11:21.270
Yes! Exactly!

00:11:21.270 --> 00:11:21.600
Exactly!

00:11:21.600 --> 00:11:22.510
You crazy woman!

00:11:22.510 --> 00:11:23.440
You crazy woman!

00:11:23.480 --> 00:11:24.240
Crazy woman!

00:11:24.360 --> 00:11:25.000
Don't escape!

00:11:25.000 --> 00:11:25.730
Crazy woman.

00:11:26.080 --> 00:11:26.510
Why are you running?

00:11:26.510 --> 00:11:27.320
Crazy woman.

00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:28.080
Come back!

00:11:28.150 --> 00:11:29.480
He's spreading rumors!

00:11:38.590 --> 00:11:39.720
I didn't expect that

00:11:41.460 --> 00:11:44.790
I would be the one transferring spiritual power to heal you.

00:11:51.840 --> 00:11:52.870
Get a good rest,

00:11:53.720 --> 00:11:54.390
Fufeng.

00:12:35.070 --> 00:12:37.550
[Bless My Lady with safe and peace]

00:12:52.710 --> 00:12:56.680
[Three years later]

00:13:09.510 --> 00:13:10.360
My Lord.

00:13:10.750 --> 00:13:12.710
These are the files

00:13:12.730 --> 00:13:14.990
Just organized today. They're all here.

00:13:15.120 --> 00:13:16.720
Thank you for your hard work.

00:13:16.720 --> 00:13:17.910
It's getting late.

00:13:18.270 --> 00:13:19.670
Why don't you rest first?

00:13:19.690 --> 00:13:22.020
It won't be too late to read them tomorrow.

00:13:22.330 --> 00:13:23.120
It's fine.

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:24.720
Yeah.

00:13:25.270 --> 00:13:26.440
Without you for a day,

00:13:26.440 --> 00:13:28.570
Yin-Yang Crossing will still be fine.

00:13:28.570 --> 00:13:29.450
You...

00:13:29.560 --> 00:13:30.350
No.

00:13:30.600 --> 00:13:33.020
Little bell, don't you know how to speak properly?

00:13:33.020 --> 00:13:33.840
My Lord

00:13:33.840 --> 00:13:36.500
Is now handling the issues of both the county yamen and Xiqianhua.

00:13:36.500 --> 00:13:38.430
Otherwise, he wouldn't be so busy.

00:13:38.910 --> 00:13:39.790
Chen Xiaohu,

00:13:40.150 --> 00:13:42.150
You're talking a lot these days.

00:13:43.250 --> 00:13:43.650
I...

00:13:43.960 --> 00:13:44.720
Alright,

00:13:44.960 --> 00:13:46.220
You guys go back to sleep.

00:13:46.220 --> 00:13:47.370
After I finish reading these,

00:13:47.370 --> 00:13:48.400
I will rest, too.

00:13:48.790 --> 00:13:49.600
-Yes. -Yes.

00:13:55.300 --> 00:13:56.160
Did I talk a lot?

00:13:56.200 --> 00:13:56.840
A lot.

00:13:57.160 --> 00:13:57.920
I think I didn't talk too much.

00:13:57.920 --> 00:13:58.690
Nope, you talked a lot.

00:13:58.690 --> 00:14:00.620
Then, I'll change it in the future.

00:15:16.390 --> 00:15:17.200
Fufeng.

00:15:28.170 --> 00:15:29.020
Where is this?

00:15:41.290 --> 00:15:42.200
Who are you?

00:15:47.200 --> 00:15:48.200
Who am I?

00:15:53.820 --> 00:15:55.350
This is Yin-Yang Crossing.

00:15:56.960 --> 00:15:57.750
And you

00:15:58.910 --> 00:16:00.240
Are Liu Fufeng.

00:16:00.980 --> 00:16:02.290
Liu Fufeng.

00:16:09.350 --> 00:16:10.780
You are my beloved.

00:17:11.599 --> 00:17:14.079
Do you want to hear a story today?

00:17:25.160 --> 00:17:26.480
Then, I'll tell you a story of

00:17:26.480 --> 00:17:28.109
A parrot.

00:17:29.750 --> 00:17:30.710
Once upon a time,

00:17:30.790 --> 00:17:32.250
There was a little parrot.

00:17:32.890 --> 00:17:35.510
It liked to hide inside the statue in the ancestral hall,

00:17:35.510 --> 00:17:36.920
And imitate human speech,

00:17:36.920 --> 00:17:38.480
Scaring the villagers.

00:17:40.270 --> 00:17:42.930
Later, there was a stubborn county magistrate.

00:17:43.110 --> 00:17:45.350
He insisted it was a man-made incident.

00:17:45.520 --> 00:17:47.640
But I thought, there are no demons in the world.

00:17:47.640 --> 00:17:50.830
There must be someone causing mischief in their guise.

00:17:51.240 --> 00:17:53.110
But that domineering local bully

00:17:53.510 --> 00:17:55.770
Always stopped him from investigating.

00:17:56.880 --> 00:17:57.740
At that time...

00:18:18.480 --> 00:18:19.590
At that time,

00:18:20.750 --> 00:18:22.110
The magistrate didn't know that

00:18:22.110 --> 00:18:23.510
The heart in his body

00:18:24.270 --> 00:18:25.880
Belonged to that bully.

00:18:26.580 --> 00:18:28.090
If you fail to find the real culprit,

00:18:28.090 --> 00:18:29.490
In three days,

00:18:29.850 --> 00:18:31.600
Whether he's a human or demon,

00:18:31.620 --> 00:18:33.680
You shall kill yourself immediately

00:18:35.240 --> 00:18:36.350
And give your heart

00:18:36.760 --> 00:18:37.770
To me.

00:18:38.640 --> 00:18:39.920
He thought,

00:18:40.160 --> 00:18:41.750
"I'm just investigating a case,

00:18:41.750 --> 00:18:43.280
And do I have to risk my life?

00:18:43.960 --> 00:18:45.490
This is too unreasonable."

00:19:00.400 --> 00:19:01.640
Is Lady Fufeng

00:19:02.510 --> 00:19:03.790
Still the same?

00:19:09.720 --> 00:19:10.890
Yes.

00:19:12.270 --> 00:19:13.160
But at least,

00:19:13.830 --> 00:19:15.630
When Lord Bai tells her stories,

00:19:15.660 --> 00:19:17.020
She listens.

00:19:20.310 --> 00:19:22.110
You don't have to worry too much.

00:19:22.160 --> 00:19:23.270
Since she woke up,

00:19:23.650 --> 00:19:25.510
She will definitely remember us.

00:19:26.930 --> 00:19:28.570
It's just hard on Lord Bai.

00:19:29.550 --> 00:19:31.920
He has to handle official business during the day,

00:19:31.920 --> 00:19:34.200
And take care of Lady Fufeng at night.

00:19:34.510 --> 00:19:37.000
I don't think he can bear it.

00:19:40.240 --> 00:19:41.030
And you?

00:19:50.370 --> 00:19:51.740
I haven't been idle.

00:19:52.060 --> 00:19:53.850
I just solved a case today

00:19:54.010 --> 00:19:55.010
All by myself.

00:19:57.730 --> 00:19:59.880
When you mortals care about others,

00:20:00.270 --> 00:20:01.530
Isn't this how you ask?

00:20:04.110 --> 00:20:05.440
You are caring about me?

00:20:19.610 --> 00:20:21.340
Which sentence shows you care?

00:21:05.950 --> 00:21:07.060
It's 7 PM.

00:21:07.570 --> 00:21:09.300
Time to report to My Lady again.

00:21:09.720 --> 00:21:11.450
That Ring Spirit named Shulang

00:21:11.510 --> 00:21:14.110
Donated the business revenue again this year.

00:21:14.790 --> 00:21:17.190
He said he had discussed it with his father.

00:21:17.750 --> 00:21:18.640
As for Xiaohu,

00:21:18.690 --> 00:21:21.190
He is learning to solve cases and do autopsies with me now.

00:21:21.190 --> 00:21:22.450
He is doing quite well.

00:21:22.650 --> 00:21:25.180
The people all call him the Master Detective.

00:21:26.400 --> 00:21:27.250
And Shuan.

00:21:27.960 --> 00:21:29.640
Though he lost his mind,

00:21:30.300 --> 00:21:32.710
He seems to still remember the county yamen.

00:21:32.710 --> 00:21:34.840
He sweeps the yamen every day,

00:21:36.000 --> 00:21:38.640
And sometimes he looks just like usual.

00:21:45.490 --> 00:21:46.400
You two,

00:21:46.880 --> 00:21:47.940
What are you doing?

00:21:48.160 --> 00:21:50.160
Do you know this is the county yamen?

00:21:51.100 --> 00:21:52.170
You deer demon!

00:21:52.270 --> 00:21:53.240
You sold me fake deer antlers!

00:21:53.240 --> 00:21:54.140
I am a deer demon.

00:21:54.140 --> 00:21:55.440
Isn't that outrageous that

00:21:55.440 --> 00:21:57.480
I'm selling deer antlers?

00:21:57.910 --> 00:22:00.550
Not to mention it's fake!

00:22:00.570 --> 00:22:01.830
You two split up first.

00:22:01.830 --> 00:22:03.400
Or I'll arrest you both.

00:22:26.960 --> 00:22:28.460
How about cutting off the other horn too,

00:22:28.460 --> 00:22:29.920
So it will be symmetrical?

00:22:30.490 --> 00:22:31.330
Good idea.

00:22:31.690 --> 00:22:32.820
Why don't you try it?

00:22:33.280 --> 00:22:34.740
Why didn't I think of that?

00:22:50.460 --> 00:22:52.900
We went to Kuquan Valley again today.

00:22:53.750 --> 00:22:56.210
I saw new shoots growing out of those cracks.

00:22:56.930 --> 00:22:57.810
I was thinking,

00:22:58.540 --> 00:23:00.410
If we sow some seeds next year,

00:23:00.690 --> 00:23:02.580
Maybe crops will grow.

00:23:03.830 --> 00:23:05.880
As for Fengling and Xiaohu...

00:23:06.000 --> 00:23:06.530
Let's go.

00:23:07.390 --> 00:23:08.450
What are you doing?

00:23:08.480 --> 00:23:09.540
What are you doing?

00:23:09.680 --> 00:23:10.240
Nothing.

00:23:10.260 --> 00:23:11.640
You don't need to worry about Fengling.

00:23:11.640 --> 00:23:13.300
Who let you walk in front of me?

00:23:13.820 --> 00:23:16.020
She's stronger than we thought.

00:23:17.430 --> 00:23:19.910
It's just that Xiaohu always provokes her.

00:23:20.830 --> 00:23:21.540
However,

00:23:21.900 --> 00:23:23.960
Fengling doesn't seem to be annoyed.

00:23:32.480 --> 00:23:34.340
There... Over there, it seems...

00:23:42.640 --> 00:23:43.480
No rush.

00:23:44.550 --> 00:23:45.350
We

00:23:46.020 --> 00:23:47.300
Have plenty of time.

00:24:23.240 --> 00:24:24.920
I've been looking for you everywhere.

00:24:24.920 --> 00:24:26.030
You are here.

00:24:28.690 --> 00:24:29.240
Here,

00:24:29.760 --> 00:24:30.820
Don't catch a cold.

00:24:33.240 --> 00:24:35.040
I'll go get you something to eat.

00:24:38.000 --> 00:24:38.830
Where did we

00:24:38.850 --> 00:24:40.510
Leave off our story last time?

00:24:42.830 --> 00:24:43.760
The local bully.

00:24:43.960 --> 00:24:44.750
Right.

00:24:45.110 --> 00:24:46.130
The local bully who always said

00:24:46.130 --> 00:24:48.240
She didn't care about anything

00:24:48.750 --> 00:24:50.010
Was truly heartbroken

00:24:50.130 --> 00:24:51.480
This time.

00:24:52.240 --> 00:24:53.510
But guess what?

00:24:54.160 --> 00:24:55.510
She still looked like

00:24:55.750 --> 00:24:57.000
She didn't care.

00:24:58.290 --> 00:24:59.950
But the Young Magistrate knew

00:25:00.190 --> 00:25:02.990
She was in great pain.

00:25:04.350 --> 00:25:05.310
He was always

00:25:05.340 --> 00:25:06.740
Worrying about her,

00:25:07.480 --> 00:25:09.520
Afraid that she would hide away alone,

00:25:09.520 --> 00:25:11.780
And she would feel no one cared about her.

00:25:12.010 --> 00:25:14.900
But there were many people who cared about her.

00:25:16.050 --> 00:25:17.780
The Young Magistrate also knew

00:25:18.510 --> 00:25:20.910
She didn't dare to show her vulnerability,

00:25:21.000 --> 00:25:22.030
Because a god

00:25:24.400 --> 00:25:25.660
Cannot be vulnerable.

00:25:50.360 --> 00:25:54.670
[Hope Lady Fufeng can return soon, Bai Shanjun.]

00:26:03.320 --> 00:26:04.650
Why is it that every time

00:26:08.310 --> 00:26:11.380
I am asked to bless myself?

00:26:12.810 --> 00:26:13.770
So strange.

00:26:20.480 --> 00:26:21.400
Lady Fufeng.

00:26:46.180 --> 00:26:47.270
Long time no see.

00:26:48.080 --> 00:26:49.320
Shouldn't you say,

00:26:50.890 --> 00:26:51.970
"Local bully,

00:26:53.540 --> 00:26:54.700
Long time no see?"

00:27:28.950 --> 00:27:30.430
You haven't answered

00:27:30.880 --> 00:27:31.880
My question.

00:27:36.940 --> 00:27:37.770
Because

00:27:40.030 --> 00:27:41.670
You are my only god.

